      "text": "FIFA Football 2004, also known as FIFA Soccer 2004 in North America, is a football simulation video game developed by EA Canada and published by Electronic Arts. It was released in October 2003 with the tagline \"Create Brilliance\".\nFIFA Football 2004 is the eleventh game in the FIFA series and the eighth to be in 3D.\nThe game is an EA Sports Bio game, and is compatible with other EA Sports games like Madden NFL 2004 and NBA Live 2004.",
